The best homemade tortillas in Scottsdale!!
Located in a historic adobe home in Old Town Scottsdale.
Dishes include ancho raspberry-encrusted pork chops and Shawnee sea bass with a cheese and rock shrimp quesadilla, topped with shoestring sweet potatoes.
The banana crisp wrapped in a sweet tortilla with blackberry compote is out of this world.

