The compote would have also been better if it had been served warm.
The whole thing was just too mushy for me.
The one thing they got right with this dish was the presentation.
It was so pretty that I took a picture before I took a bite.
One more thing they could improve on - the music.
It was a step up from elevator music.
Not what I want to hear at a dinner table.
The end.

